    "The common 4096-game block is public development evidence and can select at most one arm; it cannot confirm or promote that arm.",
    "Every endpoint must be rerun once with the identical checkpoint and seed block; exact per-game telemetry and replay-trace hashes must match before the outcome-blind input authorization can open analysis.",
